<dl id="n40176d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40176d">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40176d"> 176(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> devil leaves a / smell behind </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: In the popular mind, it seems the Devil ever leaves a filthy smell behind, this being his manner of benedition; there is, however, no Biblical allusion to demonic smells, other than references to uncleanliness. </mm> </dd></dl>
